  '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.91,"bullets":["Resolved deployment blocker related to cloud storage; DevOps confirmed fixes are now live.","Tina confirmed content is finalized and handed off to design for packaging.","Arun reported QA completion ahead of schedule, unblocking UAT which starts Monday.","Team aligned on prioritizing dashboard over export feature for this sprint.","Ravi will confirm final demo scope by Wednesday for client signoff meeting."],"highlights":[{"quote":"QA''s wrapped today, so UAT can officially start Monday.","speaker":"Arun"},{"quote":"We pushed the update last night—cloud write errors are no longer happening.","speaker":"DevOps"}],"topics":["delivery","qa","priorities"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-1106","version":1,"generated_at":"2025-11-28T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
