-- Meeting: Syncro // New North Bi-Weekly Meeting (2025-11-26 19:30:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    '18194a27-f4fd-4f8a-b974-7e8dcaea1d46',
    '2025-11-26 19:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KAETN4K5046XYW2R55HR6ANM',
    'Syncro // New North Bi-Weekly Meeting',
    '{"Brandon Garcin","Baylee Gunnell","Brandon Garcin","Igor Zagradjanin"}'::text[],
    1160,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86432186576?pwd=XxjYEV59FLfPJ9LkkJUeTlFTe1JCaL.1',
    '{"id":"01KAETN4K5046XYW2R55HR6ANM","title":"Syncro // New North Bi-Weekly Meeting","summary":{"notes":"## **Guest Booking and Outreach Strategy**\n\nThe team decided to split guest outreach between early December and January to respect holiday downtime and maximize engagement (06:19).\n\n- **Half of the guest outreach list will be contacted in early December, with the remainder in January** to avoid spamming contacts during the holiday weeks (Baylee and Brandon) (06:19).  \n    - Brandon emphasized stopping outreach by December 19th to avoid holiday spam and maintain positive relationships.  \n    - The approach balances maintaining momentum and respecting recipients’ holiday availability.  \n    - This phased outreach aims to secure January bookings while not overwhelming contacts during the busy season.  \n    - The outreach method will likely be manual due to the targeted, ABM-style list size.  \n\n- **Brandon plans to be offline the last two weeks of December (December 22 – January 2), which shapes the outreach timeline** (07:03).  \n    - Baylee will manage automated scheduling to adhere to this timeline.  \n    - Brandon’s availability influences campaign pacing and sets clear limits on active engagement periods.  \n\n- **Guest inquiries are now arriving proactively, indicating growing show recognition** (02:35).  \n    - Brandon received unsolicited requests, which Baylee is managing by forwarding to him for vetting.  \n    - This organic interest may reduce outbound effort over time and improve guest quality.  \n    - Brandon is open to quick exploratory calls with new guests to evaluate fit.  \n\n## **Content Production and Video Strategy**\n\nThe team is prioritizing higher-quality video content using Brandon’s phone setup to improve engagement and SEO impact (08:35).\n\n- **Brandon will record social video clips next week using his phone for superior quality over Riverside webcam captures** (08:35).  \n    - He intends to share raw footage via a drive folder for editing.  \n    - This shift aims to produce cleaner, more professional visuals that better support content marketing goals.  \n    - Brandon expects this to be an experiment to test video’s lift on rankings and engagement, referencing prior positive results from similar clips.  \n    - Igor and Baylee will support editing once footage is received.  \n\n- **Podcast episode publishing continues steadily, with the last episode of the year planned for December** (13:00).  \n    - Brandon plans to review the full recording before publishing and request edits if needed.  \n    - The December episode features a returning guest, Bryant, despite some technical challenges on his end with Riverside software.  \n    - Brandon manages guest technical issues as they arise but notes limitations in troubleshooting.  \n\n## **Platform and Distribution Management**\n\nThe team is effectively managing podcast distribution and exploring platform features to expand reach and engagement (11:20).\n\n- **Brandon has successfully accessed and uploaded episodes to Spotify’s platform, including testing clip uploads** (11:32).  \n    - He found the upload process straightforward and plans to experiment more with short clip uploads to enhance exposure.  \n    - Baylee and Igor provide operational support for posting and monitoring episode performance.  \n    - This platform engagement is intended to increase episode discoverability and listener engagement through multimedia.  \n\n- **Technical challenges remain with some guests’ hardware compatibility, impacting recording quality** (12:27).  \n    - Bryant’s advanced AV setup is not fully recognized by Riverside, causing inconsistent recording issues.  \n    - Brandon balances guest comfort and technical feasibility, aiming for smooth production without excessive troubleshooting.  \n\n## **Meeting Scheduling and Operational Coordination**\n\nAdjustments to meeting times are planned to improve team availability and global coordination (14:31).\n\n- **Brandon agreed to shift weekly meeting times earlier by two to three hours starting after Thanksgiving** to better align with his schedule and accommodate international contractors (14:44).  \n    - He will review his calendar and confirm the best day, noting Wednesday may have conflicts.  \n    - Baylee will follow up with calendar options after the holiday.  \n    - This change aims to enhance real-time collaboration and reduce scheduling friction across time zones.  \n\n- **There is interest in improving meeting transcription and note-taking processes through existing tools** (16:11).  \n    - Brandon is considering moving from Fireflies to Zoom’s built-in transcription to unify tools and simplify workflows.  \n    - He values privacy and participant comfort but acknowledges recording is now a common expectation.  \n    - This shift could streamline meeting documentation and action tracking across the team.  \n\n## **Resource and Time Management Around Product Launch**\n\nThe upcoming product launch is consuming significant calendar time, impacting content production schedules (08:42).\n\n- **Brandon’s availability for recording content is limited due to a product launch scheduled for Tuesday next week** (08:42).  \n    - He anticipates delays in producing social clips but plans to deliver raw footage within the week.  \n    - This prioritization reflects the business focus on the launch’s success over content output temporarily.  \n    - The team expects to catch up on pending tasks in January once the launch pressure eases.  \n\n- **Brandon’s family commitments during school breaks contribute to his time constraints** (00:00).  \n    - Working from home with children on different school schedules adds complexity to daily workflow.  \n    - He values balanced work-life integration despite current hectic periods.  \n    - This personal context underlies flexible timelines for content creation and meeting scheduling.","outline":null,"keywords":["podcast guests","holiday scheduling","social video clips","product launch","guest outreach","transcription tools"],"overview":"- **Guest Outreach Timing:** Split guest outreach in December and January to avoid holiday spamming and enhance engagement.\n- **Proactive Guest Inquiries:** Rising unsolicited guest interest may lessen outbound efforts and improve guest quality over time.\n- **Video Content Priority:** Higher-quality video content using Brandon''s phone will enhance engagement and support content marketing goals.\n- **Podcast Distribution:** Successful uploads to Spotify are ongoing; experimenting with short clips to boost engagement and discoverability.\n- **Meeting Time Adjustments:** Shifting weekly meetings earlier post-Thanksgiving to improve collaboration with international contractors.\n- **Product Launch Constraints:** Product launch next week limits content production; team aims to recover in January after event pressures.","action_items":"\n**Brandon Garcin**\nRespond to inbound podcast guest inquiry forwarded by Baylee and schedule a 15-minute call if interested (03:38)\nRecord the first social media video clip using phone next week and share raw footage with team for editing (08:42)\nReview and publish the last podcast episode of the year in December, then evaluate for any editing needs post-holiday (13:00)\nReview schedules after Thanksgiving to confirm an earlier meeting time, potentially two to three hours earlier than current 11:30 am Pacific slot (15:42)\nInvestigate Zoom’s transcription feature and consider transitioning from Fireflies for meeting recording/transcribing (18:00)\n\n**Baylee Gunnell**\nForward inbound podcast guest email to Brandon for follow-up (03:38)\nCoordinate guest outreach campaign: start sending first half of contacts in early December and pause outreach after December 19th; resume remaining contacts in January (06:05)\n\n**Igor Zagradjanin**\nAwait raw social clip footage from Brandon for editing once received (08:42)\nContinue supporting content and portal updates as needed (14:01)\n"},"duration":19.34000015258789,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"id":1,"name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"id":2,"name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"id":3,"name":"Igor Zagradjanin"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Off for a couple days at least.","index":0,"end_time":2.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":0.08,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":1,"end_time":3.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2.88,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"What days are you taking off?","index":2,"end_time":5.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3.76,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just tomorrow and Friday for the moment.","index":3,"end_time":9.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":6.96,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ll have some more time off for December holidays, but it''ll be good to.","index":4,"end_time":17.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":9.76,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Get a long weekend at least.","index":5,"end_time":19.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":17.44,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yep, I''m.","index":6,"end_time":21.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":20.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m right there with you.","index":7,"end_time":22.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":21.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"It''ll be very nice.","index":8,"end_time":23.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":22.8,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"My kids have been off of school all week and had half days all.","index":9,"end_time":28.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":24.96,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Of last week, so.","index":10,"end_time":29.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.28,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Oh, that has been a bit extra as well.","index":11,"end_time":34.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":29.48,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So it''ll be good to not also be working while wrangling that.","index":12,"end_time":38.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":34.2,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"What''s your partner''s schedule like?","index":13,"end_time":40.36,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":38.6,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Pretty similar.","index":14,"end_time":42.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":41.56,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"She''s off today, which I''m jealous of.","index":15,"end_time":46.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":42.36,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"As well as tomorrow and Friday.","index":16,"end_time":47.959,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":46.36,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But we both work from home, you know, full time, so we have all the.","index":17,"end_time":54.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":48.92,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"The benefits as well as the challenges, I suppose that come with that.","index":18,"end_time":59.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":55.24,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"With kids, it''s really the school calendar that is just not sort of designed.","index":19,"end_time":63.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":59.4,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Around having multiple working parents, which I.","index":20,"end_time":68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":63.52,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Don''T understand how anybody only has one.","index":21,"end_time":70.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":68,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Like a single income household.","index":22,"end_time":71.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":70.16,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Unless, I guess, if you''re like a fucking surgeon or something, maybe you can pull it off.","index":23,"end_time":75,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":71.76,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I don''t know who''s doing that successfully these days.","index":24,"end_time":79.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":75,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But no complaints.","index":25,"end_time":82.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":80.16,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"It''s all good.","index":26,"end_time":83.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":82.56,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"We''re doing a product launch next week.","index":27,"end_time":87.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":85.3,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So even though even the break is.","index":28,"end_time":89.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":87.3,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Sort of overshadowed by being busy and frantic and everybody trying to get stuff.","index":29,"end_time":93.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":90.02,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Ready to go and all of that.","index":30,"end_time":96.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":93.98,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But yeah, that''s very busy timing.","index":31,"end_time":98.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":96.22,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, it is, but it''s fine.","index":32,"end_time":101.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":99.06,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I remain employed, so I''m not going to complain.","index":33,"end_time":106.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":101.62,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yep, yep.","index":34,"end_time":107.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":106.26,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I don''t even know what we''ve got going on here.","index":35,"end_time":110.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":108.74,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I know we''ve been trying to figure out when to start hitting up these Microsoft experts.","index":36,"end_time":115.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":110.26,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I think our sequence is looking pretty good.","index":37,"end_time":117.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":115.64,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I have one episode back from you guys and then I think another one is getting worked.","index":38,"end_time":123.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":119.44,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So I think overall we''re in okay shape.","index":39,"end_time":126.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":123.96,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, they were looking pretty good.","index":40,"end_time":128.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":126.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''ll share my screen and we''ll just get into some of the updates.","index":41,"end_time":132.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":129.52,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So just starting off with our guest booking, seems like you have a lot of good guests scheduled right now.","index":42,"end_time":144.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":135.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I did want to bring up.","index":43,"end_time":146.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":144.79,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We had someone reach out to us, so this is actually kind of.","index":44,"end_time":150.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":146.11,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think we talked previously.","index":45,"end_time":152.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":150.71,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"You have people reaching out to you now to be on your show?","index":46,"end_time":155.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":152.87,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I have had a couple, funny enough.","index":47,"end_time":157.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":155.59,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, this one just came into our inbox so I can forward over to the email.","index":48,"end_time":162.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":158.15,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But here''s their LinkedIn.","index":49,"end_time":164.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":162.07,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So if you want them, I''ll forward you the email and you can respond to them.","index":50,"end_time":168,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":164.31,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Or you could.","index":51,"end_time":168.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":168,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"How does.","index":52,"end_time":169.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":168.92,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"How would he how would, how would this person have the like information?","index":53,"end_time":176.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":170.04,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Like how does he, how does he have our contact info to reach us?","index":54,"end_time":179.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":176.36,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"You know.","index":55,"end_time":179.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":179.2,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Good question.","index":56,"end_time":182.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":181.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Like forwarded from somebody else that we engage with potentially or.","index":57,"end_time":186.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":183.4,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Honestly I, I don''t know exactly.","index":58,"end_time":189.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":187.56,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"But there he probably like scrubbed some website or something because he found us through motion.","index":59,"end_time":196.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":189.92,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So that''s the email he sent it to.","index":60,"end_time":199.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":197.24,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So I think it might be just because like we set up your buzzsprout through motion email or something like that.","index":61,"end_time":206.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":201.4,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Sure, yeah, sure.","index":62,"end_time":208.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":206.76,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I mean it looks like a pretty good profile at a glance at least.","index":63,"end_time":212.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":208.84,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Be happy to take a 15 minute call and, and chat a little bit.","index":64,"end_time":216.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":212.32,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Why not?","index":65,"end_time":217.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":216.92,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Okay, I''ll just, I''m forwarding you the email they sent over to us right now.","index":66,"end_time":222.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":218.21,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So you, so you have that and then next.","index":67,"end_time":230.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":222.65,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, we just need to decide when we want to launch this next micro.","index":68,"end_time":233.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":230.01,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, you''re good.","index":69,"end_time":235.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":233.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We can wait a second.","index":70,"end_time":237.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":236.05,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Sorry.","index":71,"end_time":237.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":237.37,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"No, you''re good.","index":72,"end_time":238.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":237.73,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"We''re, we''re about, we''re about to lose.","index":73,"end_time":240.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":238.53,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"A tooth, so it''s a big deal.","index":74,"end_time":242.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":240.57,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Oh, that''s so exciting.","index":75,"end_time":243.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":242.61,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"My 5 year old is about to.","index":76,"end_time":245.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":244.05,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Lose her first tooth, so.","index":77,"end_time":246.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":245.37,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Oh.","index":78,"end_time":247.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":247.07,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh, she''s jumping.","index":79,"end_time":248.43,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":247.31,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Pretty, pretty, pretty important stuff.","index":80,"end_time":250.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":248.59,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Oh my goodness.","index":81,"end_time":251.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":250.55,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"The dogs ran in to growl about it.","index":82,"end_time":253.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":251.79,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"The gang''s excited.","index":83,"end_time":254.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":253.83,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Oh, that''s exciting.","index":84,"end_time":256.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":254.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I love that my, my 7 year old has lost several.","index":85,"end_time":259.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":256.59,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So it''s, you know, the challenge of being a couple years behind is always like when will I.","index":86,"end_time":263.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":259.31,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So we''ve been anxiously awaiting when Indy.","index":87,"end_time":266.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":263.71,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Will lose her first teeth.","index":88,"end_time":267.87,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":266.79,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":89,"end_time":268.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":267.87,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Start chewing on rocks so they lose them.","index":90,"end_time":271.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":268.91,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Jesus.","index":91,"end_time":272.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":272.27,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Maybe like a starburst or something, but all.","index":92,"end_time":275.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":273.15,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Not sure what you were doing as.","index":93,"end_time":279.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":278.49,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"A kid, but that was crazy.","index":94,"end_time":281.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":279.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I definitely had a couple with the old, you know, string on the door.","index":95,"end_time":285.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":282.81,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I don''t, I don''t know that they recommend doing that anymore, but I did a couple of those back in the day.","index":96,"end_time":290.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":285.89,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":97,"end_time":291.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":290.81,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Anyway, like I said, it''s been, it''s.","index":98,"end_time":293.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":291.21,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Been fun having everybody home all day.","index":99,"end_time":295.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":293.73,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":100,"end_time":296.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":295.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Busy times.","index":101,"end_time":298.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":297.37,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":102,"end_time":299.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":298.97,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So for this campaign, I think it''s just up to you what your availability looks like if, if you have the schedule to book more people in December or we can wait till January.","index":103,"end_time":309.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":299.93,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"If think you''ll be a little less.","index":104,"end_time":311.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":309.85,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Busy then I will definitely be less busy in January.","index":105,"end_time":314.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":311.67,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"In terms of bookings, I will be offline the last two weeks of the year.","index":106,"end_time":318.95,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":314.39,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So we have a little bit of.","index":107,"end_time":321.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":320.23,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"A window to try to get folks booked.","index":108,"end_time":322.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":321.19,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Now.","index":109,"end_time":323.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":322.75,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I think the question is less so about needing to or wanting to record folks in December and more do we think it is valuable to reach out to folks now with a goal of getting something scheduled to chat in January.","index":110,"end_time":337.11,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":323.11,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Or do we wait, let people come.","index":111,"end_time":339.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":337.51,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Back from the holidays, let that dust settle, because there''s always a bunch of obviously shit to deal with after the break.","index":112,"end_time":344.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":339.39,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And then do we, you know, kind of reach out to folks?","index":113,"end_time":347.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":344.53,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I could see an argument for either honestly reaching out now to try to get something on the books for January or just waiting.","index":114,"end_time":353.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":347.65,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I don''t know that I have a strong preference toward one or the other.","index":115,"end_time":357.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":354.13,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I don''t think I''m desperate to.","index":116,"end_time":359.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":357.49,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Record more people in December.","index":117,"end_time":361.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":359.01,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I think we''ve got a couple already in the hopper and we should be fine.","index":118,"end_time":364.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":361.17,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, I can see both ways to.","index":119,"end_time":368.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":365.49,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I mean, if, if we wanted to meet in the middle, we could just start with the first five contacts in December.","index":120,"end_time":375.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":368.95,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Oh.","index":121,"end_time":375.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":375.43,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"And then do the remaining five starting in January.","index":122,"end_time":378.23,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":375.83,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":123,"end_time":380.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":379.75,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And even if they miss our first outreach, you know, we''ll follow up with.","index":124,"end_time":384.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":380.27,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Those folks in January if they, if they happen to not see it.","index":125,"end_time":388.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":384.71,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, I think that could be fine.","index":126,"end_time":390.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":388.11,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Let''s just, if, if it''s automated or whatnot.","index":127,"end_time":394.07,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":391.75,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Like, I don''t know, maybe this is.","index":128,"end_time":395.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":394.07,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Actually manual, since this is a much.","index":129,"end_time":397.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":395.86,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Smaller sort of ABM approach.","index":130,"end_time":398.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":397.34,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But yeah, let''s just, let''s not write to people after like the 20th of December or something, you know, Like, I.","index":131,"end_time":405.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":398.86,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Don''T, I don''t want to be hitting people up on Christmas week or New Year''s or whatever.","index":132,"end_time":409.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":405.5,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I always am so annoyed by all the spam that I get in that window.","index":133,"end_time":412.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":409.18,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And I''m always like, just turn your automation off for two weeks and let people, like, try to, you know, hang out with their family or whatever.","index":134,"end_time":418.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":412.66,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So I don''t want.","index":135,"end_time":419.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":418.78,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"You said you''re going to be out the last two weeks of December.","index":136,"end_time":422.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":419.7,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yes.","index":137,"end_time":423.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":423.1,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"You want us to turn it off for that or just wait until December 20th.","index":138,"end_time":427.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":423.54,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, that is the 22nd through January 2nd.","index":139,"end_time":433.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":429.95,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ll be offline.","index":140,"end_time":435.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":434.11,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So.","index":141,"end_time":436.19,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":435.79,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, maybe if we are going to send stuff, maybe Friday the.","index":142,"end_time":445.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":438.99,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"19Th would be the even.","index":143,"end_time":447.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":445.99,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"That is a little close to the holidays, honestly.","index":144,"end_time":449.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":447.55,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I would say that would be.","index":145,"end_time":450.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":449.51,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"The last date that we should, you know, send anything.","index":146,"end_time":453.72,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":450.47,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":147,"end_time":455.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":454.76,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":148,"end_time":457.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":456.52,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, we''ll have it.","index":149,"end_time":458.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":457.48,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I''m less worried about, like, you know.","index":150,"end_time":461.28,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":458.88,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Response rates or whatever and more just like, ah, it''s like, I don''t know.","index":151,"end_time":465.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":461.28,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Relationships.","index":152,"end_time":466.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":465.64,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":153,"end_time":467.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":466.76,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Like, it doesn''t really matter to me if people observe Christmas or whatever.","index":154,"end_time":470.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":467.2,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"It''s just like, to me, that''s a.","index":155,"end_time":472,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":470.04,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Time of year where we should all just take a break from spamming and selling and everything that.","index":156,"end_time":478.44,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":472,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"That, you know, we all do all the time.","index":157,"end_time":480.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":478.8,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So.","index":158,"end_time":481.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":480.72,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, that sounds fine.","index":159,"end_time":481.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":481.12,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"If we want to hit half the list in the first couple of weeks of December, see if we can get some bites, great.","index":160,"end_time":486,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":481.96,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But let''s just set the expectation that.","index":161,"end_time":488.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":487.12,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"We''Re not, like, trying to put pressure on people to do anything this year.","index":162,"end_time":491.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":488.76,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, we''re trying to just make the intro and would be excited to chat with them in January if they''re interested.","index":163,"end_time":496.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":491.92,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Okay.","index":164,"end_time":497.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":497.12,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, let''s.","index":165,"end_time":498.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":497.84,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Let''s do that.","index":166,"end_time":499.44,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":498.72,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":167,"end_time":500.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":500.32,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Okay, then I''ll kick it over to.","index":168,"end_time":505.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":502.8,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"We were to chat through this.","index":169,"end_time":507.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":505.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":170,"end_time":510.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":508.94,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"These are just the social clips.","index":171,"end_time":514.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":510.78,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":172,"end_time":515.02,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":514.74,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And I think you mentioned that you''re gonna record next week.","index":173,"end_time":520.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":515.02,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"If I''m right, I''m gonna try to.","index":174,"end_time":522.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":520.22,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Get the first one out next week.","index":175,"end_time":523.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":522.14,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I have just run out of time, which I knew was gonna be a challenge on this, so that''s.","index":176,"end_time":529.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":523.06,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''m not surprised that I''ve been in that mode.","index":177,"end_time":531.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":529.3,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But it''s.","index":178,"end_time":532.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":531.74,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"It''s this product launch we have Tuesday that is particularly eating up a bunch of calendar.","index":179,"end_time":535.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":532.3,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So I will get something captured at some point next week, and I''ll.","index":180,"end_time":541.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":535.98,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ll send you guys a note.","index":181,"end_time":544.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":541.98,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ll probably host it in a drive.","index":182,"end_time":548.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":545.58,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Folder here because I don''t think I want to use Riverside.","index":183,"end_time":550.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":548.22,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I think I''ll do something that''s a little bit higher quality, like we talked about when we last met.","index":184,"end_time":555.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":550.86,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So I will get you guys a link at some point next week, let''s say to just a raw footage dump of that and we''ll see.","index":185,"end_time":563.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":555.98,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"We''ll see how it looks.","index":186,"end_time":564.74,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":563.82,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Cool.","index":187,"end_time":565.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":565.22,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"You mentioned that you''re going to record it with your just regular setup.","index":188,"end_time":570.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":565.66,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Like, do we have any maybe new ideas about that?","index":189,"end_time":572.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":570.26,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Do you maybe know which clip you''re going to record first?","index":190,"end_time":576.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":572.94,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Do you have any favorites or.","index":191,"end_time":577.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":576.38,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"So I was probably just going to go in order, but I''ll take another.","index":192,"end_time":580.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":577.74,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Look at the doc and see if.","index":193,"end_time":581.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":580.82,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Anything jumps out as being, like, more valuable than something else.","index":194,"end_time":584.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":581.78,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And yeah, I think I''ll use my phone because that''s going to be the best capture quality.","index":195,"end_time":588.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":584.82,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But, like, the framing and such will.","index":196,"end_time":590.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":588.42,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Probably be similar to what you guys.","index":197,"end_time":591.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":590.37,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"This.","index":198,"end_time":592.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":592.01,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I mean, this is what I tend to do, you know, for the podcast and all of that.","index":199,"end_time":595.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":592.37,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''m.","index":200,"end_time":597.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":596.73,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I mean, if we feel like a.","index":201,"end_time":598.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":597.17,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Virtual background or something.","index":202,"end_time":599.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":598.09,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Although my hair always clips in those and looks kind of funny.","index":203,"end_time":602.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.85,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I think this looks good enough that I''ll.","index":204,"end_time":608.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":602.93,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ll probably plan to just do the normal Setup, but it''ll look better than on Riverside because my.","index":205,"end_time":614.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":608.09,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Again, I know we talked about this a bit, but my phone just records much better than my webcam that I''m on right now.","index":206,"end_time":620.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":614.01,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yep, you''ve got a much nicer setup than most people.","index":207,"end_time":625.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":621.32,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, you think?","index":208,"end_time":626.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":625.88,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I like it.","index":209,"end_time":627.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":626.68,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I mean, it''s good.","index":210,"end_time":628.76,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":627.68,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"It''s.","index":211,"end_time":629.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":629,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"It''s well framed because there''s, like a lot of.","index":212,"end_time":631.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":629.4,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And mess and.","index":213,"end_time":632.16,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":631.32,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And, you know, piles of stuff just off of the.","index":214,"end_time":634.68,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":632.16,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"The frame here.","index":215,"end_time":636.2,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":635.08,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But it looks relatively clean compared to any other parts of my house, that''s for sure.","index":216,"end_time":643,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":636.2,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"The hidden chaos.","index":217,"end_time":645.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":644.36,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, for sure.","index":218,"end_time":647.73,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":645.64,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Just below.","index":219,"end_time":648.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":647.73,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Just below the frame here.","index":220,"end_time":650.77,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":649.09,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But, yeah, it''ll be good.","in