":0,"start_time":777.71,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So anyway, when you get too fancy, it''s like, wow.","index":276,"end_time":785.19,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":780.99,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, I''ve.","index":277,"end_time":786.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":785.19,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ve got a small little hub here that I''ve not had issues with, but.","index":278,"end_time":790.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":786.15,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, I don''t know.","index":279,"end_time":792.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":790.97,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"That''s, you know, can''t live with it.","index":280,"end_time":793.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.17,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Can''T live without it type.","index":281,"end_time":794.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":793.53,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But short clips look fine.","index":282,"end_time":797.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":796.33,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I have not watched the full episode yet.","index":283,"end_time":799.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":797.69,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I will probably publish that in December, and that''ll be probably the last episode of the year.","index":284,"end_time":804.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":799.09,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So I''ll take a closer look probably next week after the break.","index":285,"end_time":806.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":804.21,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And if.","index":286,"end_time":807.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":806.65,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"If we need any edits or.","index":287,"end_time":808.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":807.05,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Or tweaks on that, I''ll let you guys know.","index":288,"end_time":810.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.33,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"}