:945.34,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I totally get it.","index":345,"end_time":948.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":946.62,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I was chatting with some folks.","index":346,"end_time":949.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":948.62,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"We have a couple of contractors in places like Finland and other parts of the world, and it''s very hard with.","index":347,"end_time":957.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":950.46,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Me on the west coast and them.","index":348,"end_time":958.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":957.18,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Being like, you know, in the future.","index":349,"end_time":960.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":958.46,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Like the next day.","index":350,"end_time":961.91,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":960.79,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s hard to, you know, get everything aligned.","index":351,"end_time":965.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":962.23,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":352,"end_time":966.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.07,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"No stranger to that.","index":353,"end_time":967.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":966.55,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But this will be easy to move.","index":354,"end_time":969.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":967.67,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"No worries.","index":355,"end_time":969.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":969.31,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Great.","index":356,"end_time":971.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.35,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay, great follow up then.","index":357,"end_time":973.11,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":971.75,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Cool.","index":358,"end_time":974.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":973.75,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Great.","index":359,"end