"},{"text":"What?","index":374,"end_time":1003.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1003,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"What did Bailey say a minute ago about rescheduling this meeting?","index":375,"end_time":1006.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1003.32,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Bailey asked if you''d be open to.","index":376,"end_time":1015.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1013.97,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Rescheduling this meeting earlier in the day.","index":377,"end_time":1017.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1015.37,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Any day of the week, Just a couple hours earlier, if that works with your schedule.","index":378,"end_time":1021.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1017.65,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"She mentioned they could send you their.","index":379,"end_time":1023.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1021.81,"speaker_name":"Igor Zagradjanin"},{"text":"Calendar availability to help coordinate.","index":380,"end_time":1026.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1023.69,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Oh, yeah.","index":381,"end_time":1028.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1027.41,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Let''s go.","index":382,"end_time":1028.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1028.01,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Nice job, bro.","index":383,"end_time":1029.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1028.65,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"All right, cool.","index":384,"end_time":1030.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1029.89,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Well, that works.","index":385,"end_time":1031.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1030.49,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Neat.","index":386,"end_time":1033.65,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1033.09,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Anyway, I. I will at some.","index":387,"end_time":1036.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1034.21,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Again is, like, not at all urgent.","index":388,"end_time":1038.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1036.61,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I do want to get it fixed.","index":389,"end_time":1039.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1038.29,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"So I''ll.","index":390,"end_time":1039.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1039.53,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I''ll add that back to my list next week, and if I''m having trouble in there, I''ll let you know.","index":391,"end_time":1043.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1039.89,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But that''s cool.","index":392,"end_time":1044.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1043.38,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I haven''t seen my.","index":393,"end_time":1046.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1045.06,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"We use Zoom AI here, but I haven''t.","index":394,"end_time":1047.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1046.06,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"It does a really nice job of summarizing and sending actions and all that usual stuff right after the meeting ends.","index":395,"end_time":1052.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1048.26,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I have not yet seen it be something you can interact with in real time.","index":396,"end_time":1057.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1052.66,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Cool and creepy as it''s been going lately.","index":397,"end_time":1060.82,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1058.82,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":398,"end_time":1061.34,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1060.82,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yep.","index":399,"end_time":1061.86,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1061.34,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Well, I hope you guys have a wonderful Thanksgiving.","index":400,"end_time":1065.06,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1062.66,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Or at least anybody that is participating and.","index":401,"end_time":1068.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.06,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, just shoot me A reminder about rescheduling, and we can make that happen.","index":402,"end_time":1072.66,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1068.78,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, and I''ll let you guys know.","index":403,"end_time":1074.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1073.18,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Next week about a social clip or whatever.","index":404,"end_time":1075.9,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1074.14,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Quick question.","index":405,"end_time":1076.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.06,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Just about Fireflies.","index":406,"end_time":1077.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1076.66,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"So you have Zoom.","index":407,"end_time":1078.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1077.66,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Do you record your meetings with.","index":408,"end_time":1080.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1079.1,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":409,"end_time":1082.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1081.58,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Okay.","index":410,"end_time":1083.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1082.86,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":411,"end_time":1084.22,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1083.58,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I could be doing that and just toggle that on, probably.","index":412,"end_time":1088.54,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1085.58,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"And not use Firefly, since our company already pays for the Zoom transcriptions and such, so maybe I''ll do that.","index":413,"end_time":1093.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1088.54,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"But I. I don''t know.","index":414,"end_time":1095.86,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1093.82,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I. I used to not, like, just automatically recording and transcribing everything as sort.","index":415,"end_time":1100.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1095.86,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Of a. I don''t know, a courtesy.","index":416,"end_time":1102.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1100.14,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Or to, like, make the conversation feel slightly safer.","index":417,"end_time":1105.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1102.37,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"However, I feel like it is so the norm now that everything is recorded and transcribed and analyzed and all that.","index":418,"end_time":1112.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1105.45,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"That maybe people are just have come to expect it and it''s, you know, not a.","index":419,"end_time":1117.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1112.49,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Not a problem.","index":420,"end_time":1118.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1117.69,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":421,"end_time":1119.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1118.97,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":422,"end_time":1121.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1121.05,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I mean, if your company''s already paying for it, that might be.","index":423,"end_time":1123.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1121.37,"speaker_name":"Baylee Gunnell"},{"text":"I think I can toggle it on.","index":424,"end_time":1125.61,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1124.25,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"I don''t know if it''s my individual license or if it''s just on the larger team conversations that we have, which.","index":425,"end_time":1130.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1125.69,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Have, like a, you know, a shared host account.","index":426,"end_time":1132.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1130.01,"speaker_name":"Brandon Garcin"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s a good 