  '[{"text":"Receive and incorporate mortgage world content format from internal team and integrate it into the Ponce Bank website structure (26:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Christina and team to gather product specifications, rate sheets, promotional materials from all departments for website and HubSpot content development (30:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Develop marketing automation workflows and customer journey maps, incorporating feedback and distributed to participants for review (22:09)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up on issues with LOS patch integration to Salesforce and assist in exploring API or MuleSoft integration improvements (50:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with IT (Ashley) and Victor to review existing data flows and integrations for lead and product data (53:16)","completed":false},{"text":"Facilitate email communications requesting documentation and inputs from product owners by end of day following meeting (57:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Implement dashboards to report campaign engagement and business impact metrics aligned with sales results (47:01)","completed":false},{"text":"Serve as primary point of contact for collecting Ponce Bank team inputs and queries for project (57:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Coordinate with Tristan and internal resources on integrating various tracking systems like GPS and LOS with marketing and sales databases (53:16)","completed":false},{"text":"Clarify product/service definitions and collaborate on simplifying website content and language for better customer comprehension (26:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor compliance requirements for CRA educational materials and define timelines for marketing outreach to CRA segments (40:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist in defining manual versus automated touchpoints in post-onboarding customer journey to augment customer service (36:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide product matrices, marketing collateral, terms and rate sheets for respective product lines to marketing team promptly (30:53)","completed":false},{"text":"Identify key customer journeys and pain points in existing website navigation and share relevant customer insights (07:08)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
