re.","index":219,"end_time":640.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":636.83,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"We have not really found that many people are capable of figuring out how to use it on their own.","index":220,"end_time":646.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":640.55,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yep.","index":221,"end_time":648.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":647.67,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Something to kind of build momentum around that.","index":222,"end_time":653.68,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":648.47,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Like.","index":223,"end_time":654.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":653.84,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"We best practices maybe, you know, we recommend doing this.","index":224,"end_time":661.12,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.32,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"We''ve done like an onboarding sequence before.","index":225,"end_time":666.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":663.84,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Where it''s like a drip campaign.","index":226,"end_time":668.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":666.64,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"And maybe this is what you were alluding to, Eli.","index":227,"end_time":672,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":669.2,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Like, so if someone does sign up there, you know, sales can always do custom outreach as another layer.","index":228,"end_time":679.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":672,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"But then there''s also like how to get the most out of Desi Dollo.","index":229,"end_time":683.15,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":679.59,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"You know, step one, you know, where, where should I start?","index":230,"end_time":686.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":683.63,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Step two, you know, here''s, here''s how.","index":231,"end_time":689.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":686.91,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"You would do X, Y and Z.","index":232,"end_time":693.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":689.99,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"And then step three, you know, almost like, yeah, five days of Desi Dollo or something like that where you do pick the five pieces.","index":233,"end_time":702.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":693.47,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"We even have short demo videos that we''ve done before so that you''re actually diving into a portion of the application.","index":234,"end_time":709.87,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":703.31,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"And directing them to like four or five of the key features.","index":235,"end_time":713.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":709.87,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"That could be something that we look at as well.","index":236,"end_time":716.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":714.43,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"I guess we''ve also, like we said, we have kind of accepted that it''s not going to be a fully product LED approach.","index":237,"end_time":723.07,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":717.15,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"So we want to at least be demonstrating the full capability.","index":238,"end_time":728.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":723.95,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Maybe they''re not going to take advantage of the full capability on their own, but we want to kind of give them a taste of what''s available.","index":239,"end_time":737.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":729.09,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, it''s like a post registration sequence.","index":240,"end_time":740.85,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":737.81,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, we want to show them the whole menu kind of.","index":241,"end_time":743.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":741.01,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Or what''s available in Desi Dollo, things like that.","index":242,"end_time":747.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":743.97,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah, exactly.","index":243,"end_time":748.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":747.37,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Post registration sequence.","index":244,"end_time":749.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":748.05,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":245,"end_time":751.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":750.69,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So that''s something that we can map out as well.","index":246,"end_time":753.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":751.13,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"We won''t be able to do that in HubSpot because we don''t have the automated workflows.","index":247,"end_time":758.05,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":753.89,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"But we could, we could build that in an N8N.","index":248,"end_time":760.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":758.05,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"And so like someone comes through on the registration side, they could enroll in a list and we could send those emails out through an nan.","index":249,"end_time":770.06,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":760.86,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So we could effectively build that workflow there.","index":250,"end_time":773.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":770.06,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"You know, the key piece would be.","index":251,"end_time":775.62,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":774.46,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"On the content side and how.","index":252,"end_time":777.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":775.62,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"How we pick the four or five.","index":253,"end_time":779.42,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":777.82,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Best things to showcase within that time period.","index":254,"end_time":783.1,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":779.74,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"How would we get there?","index":255,"end_time":787.38,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":785.66,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Or like how would we pick those.","index":256,"end_time":789.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":787.38,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Perhaps four to five things and even develop like a short demo walkthrough video?","index":257,"end_time":794.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":789.66,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, that makes sense.","index":258,"end_time":799.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":795.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"So I''ll give you.","index":259,"end_time":801.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":800.78,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I''ll add some more feedback to the.","index":260,"end_time":803.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":801.38,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Basically also the features that we have in the freemium and maybe how to position them.","index":261,"end_time":809.42,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":803.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yep.","index":262,"end_time":810.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":809.99,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And then we can just fine tune the landing page.","index":263,"end_time":813.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":810.47,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Right.","index":264,"end_time":815.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":815.03,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So that''s one thing.","index":265,"end_time":816.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":815.67,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":266,"end_time":817.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":817.27,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So.","index":267,"end_time":817.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":817.71,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, so with the landing page we.","index":268,"end_time":819.43,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":817.87,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So Axel, when would do you think we have.",