rt_time":1316.51,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Because people are always.","index":467,"end_time":1321.07,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1319.95,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Have their phones and they''ll reply and stuff like that.","index":468,"end_time":1324.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1321.07,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So.","index":469,"end_time":1325.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1324.85,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Kind of two different schools of.","index":470,"end_time":1329.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1327.65,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Thought there who accepted my LinkedIn invite were.","index":471,"end_time":1333.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1329.21,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Not.","index":472,"end_time":1335.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1335.01,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Not all of them, but like, at least like half of them.","index":473,"end_time":1337.73,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1335.57,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"It feels like we''re Indian people as well.","index":474,"end_time":1339.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1337.73,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"I don''t know if they''re celebrating Thanksgiving yet.","index":475,"end_time":1343.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1340.05,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Maybe they are, but.","index":476,"end_time":1344.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1343.41,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, like Indian in the U.S. or Indian.","index":477,"end_time":1348.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1345.17,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah, I guess they''re all in the.","index":478,"end_time":1349.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1348.37,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"U.S. i think during the U.S.","index":479,"end_time":1351.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1349.45,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":480,"end_time":1354.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1353.81,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Well, we could.","index":481,"end_time":1354.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1354.17,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Well, when.","index":482,"end_time":1355.61,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1355.01,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"When do y'' all feel we can still just.","index":483,"end_time":1357.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1355.61,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Just move forward and enroll with that?","index":484,"end_time":1358.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1357.13,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"If we get, you know, the website up Monday and emails approved and everything, we could launch midweek.","index":485,"end_time":1369.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1360.69,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"What do y'' all think about that?","index":486,"end_time":1370.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1369.49,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Sounds perfect to me.","index":487,"end_time":1372.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1371.25,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Okay.","index":488,"end_time":1373.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1372.77,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"What do you think?","index":489,"end_time":1375.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1374.53,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"No, I just thought something really different.","index":490,"end_time":1378.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1377.18,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I thought the only time I ever celebrated Thanksgiving in the US was actually with some.","index":491,"end_time":1382.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1378.7,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"With one Indian guy who invited us.","index":492,"end_time":1384.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1382.94,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Actually.","index":493,"end_time":1387.3,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1386.94,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"You''re.","index":494,"end_time":1387.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1387.3,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"You''re destroying all of our theories right now.","index":495,"end_time":1390.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1387.66,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"It was actually the professor we stayed.","index":496,"end_time":1393.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1391.739,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"With Indian and he invited us.","index":497,"end_time":1396.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1393.98,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":498,"end_time":1397.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1396.86,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"A lot of them are obviously very nationalized in America.","index":499,"end_time":1401.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":1397.26,"speaker_name":"Eli Bebinger"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":500,"end_time":1401.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1401.18,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Well, also, it''s just two days.","index":501,"end_time":1403.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1401.58,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"People take off, so they''re.","index":502,"end_time":1404.78,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1403.18,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"They''re welcome to do that as well.","index":503,"end_time":1406.34,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1404.78,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"Because we''re pretty much does stop, but we can.","index":504,"end_time":1409.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1406.34,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"We can still keep this.","index":505,"end_time":1411,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1409.88,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"This stuff going.","index":506,"end_time":1412.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1411.16,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"All right, So I did want to add.","index":507,"end_time":1415.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1413.48,"speaker_name":"Tristan Pelligrino"},{"text":"So we.","index":508,"end_ti